title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Sep 7 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Sep 7 2022
description:
Clay and Buck break down the BYU volleyball story and compare it to the Duke lacrosse case. Cameron Sexton, Tennessee Speaker of the House talks about the Eliza Fletcher murder. Clay & Buck take a call from a former BYU basketball player and discuss her thoughts about the BYU/Duke volleyball incident. Sen. Ron Johnson (R-WI) discusses President Biden Accusing him of Targeting Social Security Benefits.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
